---
// src/components/CTA.astro
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 dark:from-green-800 dark:to-green-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Siap Mengikuti Waru Turi Fun Run 2026?</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-green-100 text-lg">Tunjukkan Race terbaik kalian dengan menjadi finisher yang akan mendapatkan medalik eksklusif. Dapatkan Achievement kalian!</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <button class="bg-white text-green-700 hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-pen mr-2"></i> Daftar Sekarang
        </button>
        <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-route mr-2"></i> Pelajari Rute
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-green-800/30 rounded-lg inline-block">
        <p class="text-green-100 text-sm"><i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i> SUPPORT CENTER</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-green-800/30 rounded-lg max-w-md mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm text-green-100">
          <i class="fas fa-user-check text-white mr-2"></i>
          <strong>M Sholeh Muchtar</strong> telah mendaftar Waru Turi Fun Run <span class="font-semibold">5K</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>